{"tid":1183758,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"米奇老鼠學位如廢紙 港女告英大學獲賠60萬","createTime":"2019-06-03T07:12:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-03T07:34:12.000Z","uid":153318,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3cfc54b3ea74189ce4766551cf49373ce37a2596","tid":1183758,"uid":153318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T07:12:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E5%A5%87%E8%B6%A3/%E7%B1%B3%E5%A5%87%E8%80%81%E9%BC%A0%E5%AD%B8%E4%BD%8D%E5%A6%82%E5%BB%A2%E7%B4%99-%E6%B8%AF%E5%A5%B3%E5%91%8A%E8%8B%B1%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E7%8D%B2%E8%B3%A060%E8%90%AC-174888?fbclid=IwAR33JsvesKqKaLM7q91PNr7fkNt-OockJdLDJUd27RcI57nd3U23pfGdvA0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fnews%2F%25E5%25A5%2587%25E8%25B6%25A3%2F%25E7%25B1%25B3%25E5%25A5%2587%25E8%2580%2581%25E9%25BC%25A0%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E4%25BD%258D%25E5%25A6%2582%25E5%25BB%25A2%25E7%25B4%2599-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%2591%258A%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%258D%25B2%25E8%25B3%25A060%25E8%2590%25AC-174888%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR33JsvesKqKaLM7q91PNr7fkNt-OockJdLDJUd27RcI57nd3U23pfGdvA0&d=oOXZKU%2BZRanU2kHQSwewOHjL6x1fkqqvETpDxuWVMK8%3D&h=35ff64f0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E5%A5%87%E8%B6%A3/%E7%B1%B3%E5%A5%87%E8%80%81%E9%BC%A0%E5%AD%B8%E4%BD%8D%E5%A6%82%E5%BB%A2%E7%B4%99-%E6%B8%AF%E5%A5%B3%E5%91%8A%E8%8B%B1%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E7%8D%B2%E8%B3%A060%E8%90%AC-174888?fbclid=IwAR33JsvesKqKaLM7q91PNr7fkNt-OockJdLDJUd27RcI57nd3U23pfGdvA0</a><br />\n<br />\n現已回港的黃博(Pok Wong，音，30歲)就讀的安格里亞魯斯金大學，屬中游級數，本港立法會議員何君堯亦為校友。她於2011年修讀國際商務策略，兩年後以一級榮譽畢業，找工作卻屢受挫敗，她斥沙紙如同廢紙，取得的只是「米奇老鼠學位」；又指該校章程宣稱「優質教育保障就業前途光明」，分明是欺騙性誤導，去年入稟倫敦縣法院，要求賠償逾6萬英鎊學費、留學開支及堂費。<br />\n<br />\n雙方日前達成庭外和解，校方如數賠償，但指黃的訴訟並無理據，章程所指就業前景不等同「合約」，校方只是聽取保險公司意見了結官司。<br />\n<br />\n黃曾指該校教學質素差，講師經常遲到或要求學生自修，甚少講解學術而一味做選擇題。她期望藉此開創先例，讓學生支付高昂學費的同時，也獲得應有的價值。米奇老鼠學位(Mickey Mouse degree)一詞，出自英前教育部長Margaret Hodge，意指那些不具學術價值、對學生職業全無幫助的學位，如高球管理、馬術心理學或冷門藝術等，然而在不少人眼中，這些課程卻如米奇老鼠般惹人喜愛。"},{"pid":"698242bb8924093afcb8e2e170bcfd07eabd1802","tid":1183758,"uid":40470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T07:14:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nIVE仔發達機會"},{"pid":"d2e9ad0dd72ed895ef5f76888eced600881f0643","tid":1183758,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T07:16:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7a30413d58e2f5c8e6ca017cb2895177beb1bcb","tid":1183758,"uid":51271,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T07:16:30.000Z","msg":"<strong>本港立法會議員何君堯亦為校友</strong><br />\n<br />\nCall佢啦"},{"pid":"a4ab2eff05708d01fc208fc5ee9401cf4cef4a13","tid":1183758,"uid":139187,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T07:16:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BJ7Jpe8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBJ7Jpe8.jpg&h=9078e752&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2f419f72f8e801c1c0bba2fa14dae84565c9ad33","tid":1183758,"uid":123848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T07:17:12.000Z","msg":"讀完可以拎番學費咁正<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9441e9947b5877e8f218afd3af529f989eca8553","tid":1183758,"uid":61882,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T07:23:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/QitYJ5zBKmw/hqdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FQitYJ5zBKmw%2Fhqdefault.jpg&h=53adf016&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n小熊維尼學位威啲"},{"pid":"de1df41dfd2dc96bf99fe5019574345ef1663db0","tid":1183758,"uid":18395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T07:23:43.000Z"